'''Ventra'''是美國[[芝加哥交通局|芝加哥交通局]]和{{link-en|Pace (交通)|Pace (transit)|Pace}}的電子支付系統，並取代{{link-en|芝加哥卡|Chicago Card}}和交通卡自動收費系統。Ventra（以拉丁文「大風」命名，但實際拉丁文拼作「ventosa」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metroplanning.org/news-events/article/6548|title=Talking Transit: Chicago transit gets open payment system|last=Mancini Nichols|first=Chrissy|date=2012-10-22|publisher=Metropolitan Planning Council|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130405091957/http://www.metroplanning.org/news-events/article/6548|archivedate=2013-04-05|accessdate=2013-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>）於2013年8月推出，並於2014年7月完成全系統過渡<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ventrachicago.com/faq/|title=Ventra FAQ|publisher=CTA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019155026/https://www.ventrachicago.com/faq/|archivedate=2013-10-19|accessdate=2013-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=JulyRollout/>。該卡包括數個支付方法，如[[射頻識別|射頻識別]]（RFID）的[[非接觸式智能卡|非接觸式智能卡]]、單日或單次使用的RFID車票，任何個人銀行發出帶有RFID的信用卡或借記卡，以及兼容的[[手機|手機]]<ref name="CTAVentra">{{cite web|url=http://www.transitchicago.com/ventra/|title=Ventra|publisher=CTA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014044446/http://www.transitchicago.com/ventra/|archivedate=2013-10-14|accessdate=2013-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.redeyechicago.com/news/cta/redeye-ventra-payments-using-phone-personal-bank-card-20140529,0,3282258.story|title=How to make Ventra payments using phone, personal bank card|last=Swartz|first=Tracy|date=2014-05-29|publisher=Redeye Chicago|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703135448/http://www.redeyechicago.com/news/cta/redeye-ventra-payments-using-phone-personal-bank-card-20140529%2C0%2C3282258.story|archivedate=2014-07-03|accessdate=2014-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TtgOuuLxn_Q|title=Google Wallet on Ventra - It's live!|publisher=youtube|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328081626/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TtgOuuLxn_Q|archivedate=2014-03-28|accessdate=2014-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Ventra由{{link-en|立方交通系統|Cubic Transportation Systems}}營運<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.fastcoexist.com/3058075/this-amazing-app-could-integrate-every-urban-transportation-system-and-pay-you-not-to-drive|title=This Amazing App Could Integrate Every Urban Transportation System—And Pay You Not To Drive|last=Mendelson|first=Zoe|date=2016-03-23|work=Fast Company|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503032524/http://www.fastcoexist.com/3058075/this-amazing-app-could-integrate-every-urban-transportation-system-and-pay-you-not-to-drive|archivedate=2016-05-03|accessdate=2020-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。手機app容許用戶管理車費、購買月票和購買[[芝加哥城市鐵路|芝加哥城市鐵路]]的移動車票。
